            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ", the driver pushed the car hard along the Hollywood Freeway, wound throw tight residential streets, and did everything he could think of ",
            "type": "text",
